<% content_for :title do %>Security — Lint<% end %>
<% content_for :meta_description do %>How Lint protects your code: local-first, encrypted in transit and at rest, audit logs, GDPR compliance.<% end %>

<section class="relative isolate py-16 md:py-20 overflow-hidden">
  <div aria-hidden="true"
       class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-32 -right-32 -z-10 h-[560px] w-[560px] rounded-full"
       style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(34,211,238,0.18) 0%, rgba(34,211,238,0) 70%);"></div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 space-y-10">
    <header>
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/30 text-brand-300 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        Security
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white leading-[1.05]">Security & Compliance.</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 text-base md:text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
        Security by design, encryption end to end, principle of least privilege, full traceability.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-6">
        <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-300">Protection</div>
        <ul class="mt-2 text-slate-300 text-sm list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>System hardening, patching</li>
          <li>Encryption in transit & at rest</li>
          <li>Secret management (KMS)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-6">
        <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-300">Access</div>
        <ul class="mt-2 text-slate-300 text-sm list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>IAM & RBAC</li>
          <li>SSO (OAuth, SAML)</li>
          <li>Least-privilege principle</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-6">
        <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-300">Resilience</div>
        <ul class="mt-2 text-slate-300 text-sm list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>Backups & restoration drills</li>
          <li>Audit logging & traceability</li>
          <li>Pen-tests & internal reviews</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/30 to-brand-700/30 border border-brand-500/30 p-8">
      <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">Local-first by default</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-slate-200 leading-relaxed">Your code never leaves your machine unless you explicitly opt into Lint Cloud. The CLI runs offline, the server is open-source and self-hostable, and the cloud is opt-in.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-8">
      <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">Report a vulnerability</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">Found a security issue? Email <a href="mailto:security@osmove.com" class="text-brand-300 hover:text-brand-200 underline">security@osmove.com</a>. We respond within 48 business hours. PGP available on request.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
